{"type":null,"faqId":18037,"title":"荣耀3C 4G版 Emui3.0信息列表排序不按照时间排序或信息置顶功能？","answer":"<p>原因分析：<br>\n在会话列表界面，信息默认按照时间排序。<br>\n信息模块支持“置顶”功能，可以将某个会话置顶显示（长按某条会话，在Menu菜单中有“置顶”选项）。对于“置顶”显示的信息，右上角有一个绿色三角标记。对于其他非置顶信息依然按照时间排序。<br>\n解决方案：<br>\n取消置顶功能（长按某条会话，在Menu菜单中有“取消置顶”选项）。<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"807","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1420446258000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":18,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀3C,4G版,EMUI3.0,3.0,信息,排序,时间","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}